 *

import 'dart:io'; void main() { int a, b, c, gcd = 1; print("enter the two number for the gcd to be found out"); a = int.parse(stdin.readLineSync()!); b = int.parse(stdin.readLineSync()!); if (a > b) { c = b; } else { c = a; } for (int i = 1; i <= c; i++) { if (a % i == 0 && b % i == 0) { gcd = i; } } print("the greatest common divisor is $gcd"); }
